# Local agent-CLI dev environment — not part of the distributable repo.
# Exception: the studio-level librarian agent (spec 002) is a committed, static
# file so any machine gets the same knowledge keeper (Art VII multi-machine).
# Negation must re-include each parent dir before the one file can be un-ignored.
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/agents/
.claude/agents/*
!.claude/agents/librarian.md
